WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.292
Your mandate is to develop conflict-agility. When a team member

00:00:04.292 --> 00:00:08.584
proposes a solution, demand that they state their claim, provide

00:00:08.584 --> 00:00:12.876
the supporting evidence, and articulate the questions it provokes. Treat

00:00:12.876 --> 00:00:17.167
their explanations as thinking events. You must then map the

00:00:17.167 --> 00:00:21.459
specific variables of the dispute to the correct resolution strategy:

00:00:21.459 --> 00:00:25.751
Problem-solving, Smoothing, Forcing, Compromising, or Withdrawing.
